    <title>HExo安装及优化流程</title>
    <url>/Next-install/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>本博客使用Next主题(8.22版)</p>
<hr>
<h3 id="准备工作"><a href="#准备工作" class="headerlink" title="准备工作"></a>准备工作</h3><p>下载安装 node.js  <a href="https://nodejs.org/en/" title="[最好的markdown教程](https:&#x2F;&#x2F;nodejs.org&#x2F;en&#x2F;)">官网下载</a>。<br>下载安装 git <a href="https://git-scm.com/downloads" title="[最好的markdown教程](https:&#x2F;&#x2F;git-scm.com&#x2F;downloads">官网下载</a></p>
<p>1、本地搭建 hexo 静态博客</p>
<ul>
<li>安装 hexo 框架: 打开 cmd 运行</li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install -g hexo-cli</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<ul>
<li>新建一个文件夹，如 Blog ，进入该文件夹内，右击运行 git ，输入：</li>
</ul>
 <figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo init</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p><strong>注意</strong>：如果初始化失败（github连接失败），可以在git中添加代理</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">### 添加代理</span><br><span class="line">git config --global http.proxy &quot;http://127.0.0.1:8080(更改为自己的端口)&quot;</span><br><span class="line">git config --global https.proxy &quot;http://127.0.0.1:8080(更改为自己的端口)&quot;</span><br><span class="line">### 取消代理</span><br><span class="line">git config --global --unset http.proxy</span><br><span class="line">git config --global --unset https.proxy</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<ul>
<li>注意：添加后记得重启（反正我没重启然后搞了半天都没找到原因）</li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git config -l --global //重启</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<ul>
<li>生成完 hexo 模板，安装 npm ，运行：</li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>博客的主体部分到此已经完成了，来看看效果吧。运行：</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo server</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>复制提示中的地址 localhost:4000 <a href="localhost:4000" title="[默认页面](localhost:4000)">默认页面</a>，在浏览器中打开，会显示默认页面</p>
<h3 id="添加主题"><a href="#添加主题" class="headerlink" title="添加主题"></a>添加主题</h3><ul>
<li>下载next主题，在<strong>根目录</strong> （Blog）运行下面的命令</li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git clone https://github.com/next-theme/hexo-theme-next</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>后续部分参考链接： <a href="https://www.philoli.com/building-a-blog-from-scratch/" title="从零开始搭建 Hexo 博客简明教程（2024版）">从零开始搭建 Hexo 博客简明教程（2024版）</a></p>
<h3 id="优化指南"><a href="#优化指南" class="headerlink" title="优化指南"></a>优化指南</h3><ul>
<li><p>Pisces风格设置横向导航栏<br>参考本站链接：<a href="http://localhost:4000/Pisces-nav/">Next主题Pisces风格状态栏调整</a></p>
</li>
<li><p>添加相关文章:下载插件</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-related-posts --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>修改主题配置文件<code>_config.yml</code>enable:为true</p>
</li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">related_posts:</span><br><span class="line">  enable: true</span><br><span class="line">  # Custom header, leave empty to use the default one 设置推荐区块的标题</span><br><span class="line">  title:   </span><br><span class="line">  display_in_home: false</span><br><span class="line">  params:</span><br><span class="line">    maxCount: 5</span><br><span class="line">    #PPMixingRate: 0.0</span><br><span class="line">    #isDate: false</span><br><span class="line">    #isImage: false</span><br><span class="line">    #isExcerpt: false</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>在主题配置文件中<code>_config.yml</code>中添加以下代码</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">related_posts:</span><br><span class="line">    enabled: true</span><br><span class="line">    enable_env_name: prod</span><br><span class="line">    filter_threshold: 0.3</span><br><span class="line">    related_count: 3</span><br><span class="line">    weight:</span><br><span class="line">        title: 0.05</span><br><span class="line">        description: 0.05</span><br><span class="line">        keywords: 0.01</span><br><span class="line">        tags: 0.005</span><br><span class="line">        categories: 0.005</span><br><span class="line">        text: 1</span><br><span class="line">    stemmers:</span><br><span class="line">      - en</span><br><span class="line">      - ru</span><br><span class="line">    reserved:</span><br><span class="line">      - asp.net</span><br><span class="line">      - vs.net</span><br><span class="line">      - ado.net</span><br><span class="line">      - .net</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<ul>
<li>添加推荐文章<br>在主题配置文件下面添加如下字段</li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">recommend_posts:</span><br><span class="line">  - title: HExo安装及优化流程  #文章名字</span><br><span class="line">    url: /Next-install/       #文章链接</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<ul>
<li>然后把<code>Blog\themes\next\source\css\_common\outline\sidebar\related-posts.styl</code>文件复制到<code>Blog\themes\next\layout\_partials\sidebar</code>改名为<code>post-recommend.njk</code><br>替换为如下代码</li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;div class=&quot;links-of-blogroll-title&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">   &lt;span&gt;推荐文章&lt;/span&gt;</span><br><span class="line">  &#123;%- if theme.related_posts.icon %&#125;&lt;i class=&quot;&#123;&#123; theme.related_posts.icon &#125;&#125; fa-fw&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#123;% endif %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;ul class=&quot;popular-posts&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&#123;%- for post in theme.recommend_posts %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">  &#123;%- set popular_post = site.posts.findOne(&#123; path: path &#125;) %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">  &lt;li class=&quot;popular-posts-item&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;a class=&quot;popular-posts-link&quot; href=&quot;&#123;&#123; post.url &#125;&#125;&quot; rel=&quot;bookmark&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &#123;&#123; post.title &#125;&#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#123;%- if popular_post.date %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">     &lt;time class=&quot;popular-posts-time&quot;&gt;&#123;&#123; date(popular_post.date) &#125;&#125;&lt;/time&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &#123;%- endif %&#125;  </span><br><span class="line">    &lt;/a&gt;</span><br><span class="line">  &lt;/li&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&#123;%- endfor %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;/ul&gt; </span><br><span class="line">&lt;/div&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="添加加密文章"><a href="#添加加密文章" class="headerlink" title="添加加密文章"></a>添加加密文章</h3><p>安装插件<code>hexo-blog-encrypt</code></p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install --save hexo-blog-encrypt</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<ul>
<li>将 “password” 字段添加到您文章信息头.</li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">title: Hello World</span><br><span class="line">date: 2016-03-30 21:18:02</span><br><span class="line">password: hello</span><br><span class="line">---</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<ul>
<li>修改系统配置文件，在结尾添加如下信息</li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">  #文章加密</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"># Security</span><br><span class="line">encrypt: # hexo-blog-encrypt</span><br><span class="line">  abstract: 有东西被加密了, 请输入密码查看.</span><br><span class="line">  message: 您好, 这里需要密码.</span><br><span class="line">  tags:</span><br><span class="line">  - &#123;name: tagName, password: 密码A&#125;</span><br><span class="line">  - &#123;name: tagName, password: 密码B&#125;</span><br><span class="line">  wrong_pass_message: 抱歉, 这个密码看着不太对, 请再试试.</span><br><span class="line">  wrong_hash_message: 抱歉, 这个文章不能被校验, 不过您还是能看看解密后的内容.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<ul>
<li>文章不加密：设置<code>password=&quot;&quot;</code>即可</li>
</ul>
<h3 id="评论系统"><a href="#评论系统" class="headerlink" title="评论系统"></a>评论系统</h3><ul>
<li><p>Livere（来必力）评论插件:参考链接如下 <a href="https://ericasun.github.io/2024/03/18/hexo/2024/Hexo%E6%B7%BB%E5%8A%A0%E8%AF%84%E8%AE%BA%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9Flivere/">Hexo添加评论系统livere</a></p>
</li>
<li><p>开启 Utterances 评论功能<br> 创建存放 comments 的代码仓库，必须为 public，且可创建 issue。<br> 点击这个链接安装 utterances app 到刚刚创建的那个仓库<br><a href="https://github.com/apps/utterances">install utterances app</a> 点击这个链接安装 utterances app 到刚刚创建的那个仓库<br>点击安装，选择你用来存放评论的库，选择相应的权限，点击保存<a href="https://blog.lanweihong.com/posts/24011/">参考链接</a></p>
<ul>
<li>修改主题配置文件：找到以下位置</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># Utterances</span><br><span class="line"># For more information: https://utteranc.es</span><br><span class="line">utterances:</span><br><span class="line">  enable: true</span><br><span class="line">  repo: 用户名/仓库名称 # 评论系统仓库mingc</span><br><span class="line">  # Available values: pathname | url | title | og:title</span><br><span class="line">  issue_term: pathname</span><br><span class="line">  # Available values: github-light | github-dark | preferred-color-scheme | github-dark-orange | icy-dark | dark-blue | photon-dark | boxy-light</span><br><span class="line">  theme: github-light</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"># Isso</span><br><span class="line"># For more information: https://isso-comments.de</span><br><span class="line">isso: # &lt;data_isso&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>注意：参考链接中NEXT主题为老版本，新版本（8.0+）已集成Utterances评论系统，按照上面配置启用即可。</p>
<h1 id="完成上边操作后需要素质三联hexo-clean-hexo-g-hexo-s"><a href="#完成上边操作后需要素质三联hexo-clean-hexo-g-hexo-s" class="headerlink" title="完成上边操作后需要素质三联hexo clean &amp;&amp; hexo g &amp;&amp; hexo s"></a>完成上边操作后需要素质三联<code>hexo clean &amp;&amp; hexo g &amp;&amp; hexo s</code></h1>]]></content>
